                            <comment id="13639735" author="rajith" created="Tue, 23 Apr 2013 22:37:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If we move the close connection method inside a finally block, then we can ensure the TCP connection is closed, even if an exception is thrown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;+                    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt;
+                    {
+                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;
+                        {
+                            _delegate.closeConnection(timeout);
+                        }
+                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (Exception e)
+                        {
+                            _logger.warn(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Error closing underlying protocol connection&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, e);
+                        }
+                    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13640518" author="gemmellr" created="Wed, 24 Apr 2013 14:58:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seems reasonable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13641879" author="rajith" created="Thu, 25 Apr 2013 15:07:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have checked in a fix at &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1475810&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1475810&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should we include this in 0.22 ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13644479" author="justi9" created="Mon, 29 Apr 2013 13:35:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reviewed by Robbie.  Approved for 0.22.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13645788" author="rajith" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 18:01:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Applied patch to the 0.22 branch.&lt;br/&gt;
See &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1477705&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1477705&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
